metadata.name: MoZ Bingo 1/175
metadata.description:
Are you a fan of Moment of Zen?

Are you looking to revivify your listening / viewing experience? 

To quit life as a passive consumer and embrace active participation?

If you answered, "yes. Yes. YES!" to the questions above, then this is the game for you.

We've upgraded and enhanced legacy bingo technology to conform with the bleeding edge advancements of World Wide Web3.0, offering a truly immersive companion to the best in audio-visual edutainment. 

Meticulously crafted to ensure backward compatibility; future-proofed for new episodes. It puts the fun back in non-fungible token.

Unabashedly and uncompromisingly unofficial and unaffiliated. 

And because it's on The Blockchain, it's unalterable and undeniably yours.

Here's the alpha: be an Alpha and mint today.
